### 成员 A 第一阶段接口测试清单
### 使用方式：先启动后端服务，登录后把 token 填到下面变量

@baseUrl = http://127.0.0.1:8000
@token = 替换为登录返回的token
@recordId = 1
@threadId = 替换为生成接口返回的thread_id
@knowledgeFileId = 1

### 1. 首次生成：应扣 1 次，创建 name_records 和 usage_records
POST {{baseUrl}}/names/generate
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "category": "企业名",
  "surname": "",
  "gender": "不限",
  "length": "两字",
  "other": "AI 起名工具，科技感，亲和力",
  "exclude": []
}

### 2. 多轮反馈：不扣次数，创建 name_feedbacks，更新 name_records.result_data
POST {{baseUrl}}/names/feedback
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "thread_id": "{{threadId}}",
  "category": "企业名",
  "feedback": "名字更短一些，更有科技感"
}

### 3. 历史列表：只能看到自己的记录
GET {{baseUrl}}/names/records?skip=0&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. 历史详情：应返回 feedbacks
GET {{baseUrl}}/names/records/{{recordId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 5. 删除历史记录：软删除
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/names/records/{{recordId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 6. 上传知识库文件：应返回 knowledge_file_id 和 pending 状态
POST {{baseUrl}}/knowledge/upload
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="company_rules.txt"
Content-Type: text/plain

企业命名要求：简洁、科技感、避免生僻字。
--boundary--

### 7. 知识库文件列表：查看 pending / processing / completed / failed
GET {{baseUrl}}/knowledge/files?skip=0&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 8. 知识库文件详情
GET {{baseUrl}}/knowledge/files/{{knowledgeFileId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}